Subject: Request for Work From Home and Leave

Dear [HR's Name],

I hope this email finds you well.

I am writing to request approval for work-from-home arrangements from 6th January to 10th January due to [brief reason, e.g., personal circumstances, travel, etc.]. Additionally, I would like to request a leave for 13th January for [brief reason, e.g., personal commitments, health, etc.].

I will ensure that all my responsibilities and tasks are managed efficiently during the work-from-home period, and I will coordinate with my team to avoid any disruptions. Please let me know if you need any additional details or if there are specific formalities I need to complete.

Thank you for considering my request. I look forward to your response.

Best regards,
[Your Full Name]
[Your Job Title]
[Your Contact Information, if necessary]


---

Feel free to modify the reasons as per your situation!
